a:5:{s:5:"title";s:53:"Scoro v26.1 cleans up old notifications automatically";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:374:"<p>From version 26.1, Scoro removes notifications older than two years across sites. This is presented as a performance improvement. The cleanup affects notifications only, not the records the notifications reference.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/">https://www.scoro.com/blog/scoro-version-update-26-1/</a></p>
